l you sacrifice the living in the hope of bringing her back? Your decisions will shape the fate of New Eden’s inhabitants - may they be living or dead, and determine the end of your journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLAME</strong> the living and sacrifice their lives, holding them responsible for their actions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BANISH</strong> souls of the departed, condemning them to eternal suffering </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ASCEND</strong> souls, liberating them from eternal sorrow and granting them serenity</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493640/extras/82c28ca4408f17d8f0878a4621cf9353.webp?t=1763044792\" width=616 height=46 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493640/extras/6aa2d3ef5437402a57c6a8d1639ede6a.poster.avif?t=1763044792\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493640/extras/6aa2d3ef5437402a57c6a8d1639ede6a.webm?t=1763044792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1493640/extras/6aa2d3ef5437402a57c6a8d1639ede6a.mp4?t=1763044792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Banishers are specialized in combat against undead creatures, such as specters or ghosts. Combine Red's physical arsenal with Antea's supernatural powers in a dynamic combat system. Find your own style by mixing weapon attacks and spiritual abilities. Powerful synergies will lead you to defeat New Eden’s most dangerous enemies and bosses. </p><p class=\"bb_parag